entries.s_13fcbd87: Psst! Hey you! Yeah you! C'mere. You look as if you'd be suitable to join Jabba's forces. But keep your voice down. The Empire rules this place and doesn't take kindly to members of the Hutt family.
entries.s_19ca58d8: You're not very exciting. I'll wait for someone else, then. Bye!
entries.s_1c6f5661: You don't have enough money. Are you trying to jip me? Who do you think I am? Get out of here!
entries.s_241afd0a: I didn't expect you to have the money. You're just a commoner, afterall.
entries.s_32a1ecd: Look at that. You actually have the money. Well, you didn't specify if you wanted a direct location, so I gave you a general location instead! HAHA! So long, sucker!
entries.s_38bef1fe: What?! You don't have the money? Ugh! Go away!
entries.s_3a28c7c4: That's a sad story. I'll find someone else to buy my information, then.
entries.s_5abff6d6: I ought to give you the location for free just to see you get a whoopin'! HA! Anyway, the Tusken Bunker is on sale for 30 credits. How about it?
entries.s_5d7da0: Thank you! Here's your information. Now, get lost. I have other business to attend to.
entries.s_5ee77a06: That'll be, uh.. 20 credits? No--60 credits!
entries.s_63855d3f: Oh, look at that. I don't have the money.
entries.s_6892af1b: I hope the Hutts find you and bury you in the desert!
entries.s_6b184c6: You're so cheap! I'm desperate here! You think I'm going to sell out my own people for less than 60 credits? You're nuts! Get lost!
entries.s_6cf09e8e: That'll be 15 credits. Do you have the money?
entries.s_72ac291d: I can already tell that I don't want to get into this mess.
entries.s_74ed5d50: 60 credits, please. And don't think about cheating on me, here. This information is dangerous to be passing around, especially without pay.
entries.s_88788d03: Pfft! Go away. I see another client. I can't waste my time with you.
entries.s_9ac6e8f5: Well, you'd have to talk to Jabba about that. I can't just sign you up. But I can tell you the location of our hideout. Maybe you can scope it out and see if you like it. It's gonna cost you, though. In fact, I have a couple of places you might be interested in.
entries.s_aae6686e: Excellent! The information has been downloaded. Thank you for your business! I hope you can find it okay! You should have paid for a direct location. HAH!
entries.s_b81c8c9: I'll find someone else to buy my information!
entries.s_c599cc9e: Oh. Well, come back when you do. I have other deals to conduct.
entries.s_c799721b: Ahh! I will download the information into your datapad. Thank you for your business!
entries.s_c9a787f0: Fine, then. Get lost. I'm trying to run a business here.
entries.s_d0c6151b: Sorry, don't have any credits on me.
entries.s_d9903b42: Yes, I do. Here you are.
entries.s_e3dda380: I should--ugh! You don't have enough money! Get lost, you cheapskate!
entries.s_ea388738: I'll give you the information for... 50 credits.
entries.s_f026df25: First, the Hutt Hideout. Yeah, I know. Selling out my own people. I have to make a living, you know! I also have information regarding the Rebel Military Base and a Tusken Bunker. What do y'say?
